<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٠٨ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4563">عَلِيُّ بْنُ عَبْدِ اللهِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2478">سُفْيَانُ </a>قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4822">عَمْرٌو: </a>أَخْبَرَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4385">عَطَاءٌ </a>: سَمِعَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1091">جَابِرًا </a><span class="special">﵁</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«كُنَّا نَعْزِلُ وَالْقُرْآنُ يَنْزِلُ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>